{"tid":793872,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"🙇🏾‍♀急問🙇🏾‍♀各位freshmen典樣準備開學裝束，如何避免隔日同一件衫？？？？？","createTime":"2018-08-25T17:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T03:03:18.000Z","uid":69289,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"be557ac4194123065be3df8f49221085d4b7eb8b","tid":793872,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"姐係咁，平時著開一大堆印花圖案T既我，發覺同普遍大學生裝束有啲唔同<br />\n<br />\n想話趁仲有一個星期執執佢，究竟衫褲鞋襪應該點解決好，唔想比人認出冇衫換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講下我依家有咩先：<br />\n<br />\n衫，印花圖案T，運動T<br />\n<br />\n褲，有4件粗著既，長既多數係行出type，短就落街運動綿質布料type<br />\n<br />\n鞋，我有三對，其中一對係平時體育堂對波鞋(偏白色)，另外兩對係行出鞋(算係貴野黍)<br />\n<br />\n襪，以前中學著開有五對，尋日去左M&amp;S買左pack深色長襪，同埋買左幾對短既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫下手，錢不太大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a743981b07991c422234ac86de386905f99c6095","tid":793872,"uid":135178,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"日日着同一件"},{"pid":"2e91c896f9d7dad8988ae15e09c7705265514786","tid":793872,"uid":53652,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:27:43.000Z","msg":"日日著ocamp tee <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e404036cae024683ff5fd367eee061a05cca51ca","tid":793872,"uid":66339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:28:13.000Z","msg":"撞衫咪有話題，咪可以做fd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b036544585d391cea657ff3a6b01ea040c993f7","tid":793872,"uid":15863,"li